@startuml MDS Application Architecture
title MDS Application Management System — Class Diagram\nwith Design-Flaw Annotations

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam nodesep 60
skinparam ranksep 50
skinparam classFontSize 11
skinparam packageFontSize 13

' ============================================================================
' LEGEND
' ============================================================================
legend bottom left
  |= Symbol |= Meaning |
  |<#FFCCCC> Red class | Design flaw / SOLID violation |
  | **<<flaw>>** | Annotated architectural smell |
  | --|> | Inheritance |
  | *-- | Composition |
  | ..> | Dependency (uses / calls) |
  | FK CASCADE | Foreign key with ON DELETE CASCADE |
endlegend

